  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-provider RPC aggregation with intelligent routing",
    "HTTP and WebSocket JSON-RPC proxy support",
    "Circuit breakers and automatic failover",
    "Real-time provider benchmarking and selection",
    "WebSocket subscription multiplexing with gap-filling",
    "Geo-distributed clustering for observability",
    "Profile-based multi-tenancy",
    "LiveView dashboard for monitoring"
